descriptions.en: Reduces the HP of sleeping opposing Pokémon.
descriptions.fr: Inflige des dégâts aux ennemis endormis.
descriptions.es: Inflige daño a cualquier rival que esté dormido.

descriptions.en: Boosts the Pokémon’s Speed stat in rain.
descriptions.fr: Augmente la Vitesse du Pokémon s’il pleut.
descriptions.ko: 비가 오는 날씨일 때 스피드가 올라간다.

descriptions.en: The Pokémon’s proud of its powerful pincers. They prevent other Pokémon from lowering its Attack stat.
descriptions.fr: Le Pokémon est armé de lames tranchantes qui font sa fierté et empêchent son Attaque de baisser.
descriptions.it: L’Attacco del Pokémon non può diminuire grazie alla morsa micidiale in cui è in grado di stringere i nemici.
descriptions.de: Hindert Angreifer durch mächtige Scheren daran, den Angriffs-Wert zu senken.
descriptions.es: Evita que el rival le baje el Ataque.
descriptions.ko: 힘이 자랑인 집게를 가지고 있어 상대가 공격을 떨어뜨리지 못한다.
